❤️ Roblox Buddy AI Anniversary Event Overview 

The Roblox Buddy AI Anniversary Event celebrates both the website's anniversary and Buddy's birthday on the same day.

This event focuses on fun, teamwork, friendship, party activities, and community celebrations rather than competition alone.

Unlike Halloween (Horror) or Christmas (Winter Celebration), the Anniversary Event is a giant birthday party where every player helps Buddy celebrate.

